{"tid":1968581,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【國際戰線】識外語嘅全部同我入嚟！！！！！","createTime":"2020-04-11T18:32:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-12T02:08:16.000Z","uid":54653,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"9c678b6c4dbf515098057c7391d38522990f8fc3","tid":1968581,"uid":54653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T18:32:42.000Z","msg":"話說小弟最近日日喺屋企好撚悶 <br />\n上咗啲討論區吹水 諗住溝下架妹<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n點知好多架仔架妹同韓國人（至少有3個）知我係香港人<br />\n都問我香港而家點，係咪放棄咗反送中<br />\n<br />\n我答佢而家命仔緊要，雖然冇大型活動<br />\n但仲有文宣戰線，live集會等！！仲未完！<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/X40giAs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FX40giAs.png&h=50b3f5e6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HvAsqft.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHvAsqft.jpg&h=efa1b8c9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n（其他圖唔記得咗cap，得兩張將就下）<br />\n佢哋聽完都明點解我哋靜咗<br />\n仲話如果而家感染死咗就冇香港後代<br />\n同埋佢哋本身唔知中國禁咗動森<br />\n知道咗嘅反應係：咁和平嘅game都禁?!<br />\n其實佢哋好多都支持香港人 有個韓仔仲同我講時代革命<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又話點解習近平冇感染到武漢肺炎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我知而家係靜咗好多，但日日喺屋企咁得閒<br />\n識外語嘅不妨去同外國人吹下水<br />\n練下外語順便向外宣傳下<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74acea8b00658e0392fcb2090513d2bd08073647","tid":1968581,"uid":54653,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T18:49:33.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=KH4FjILxiUM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DKH4FjILxiUM&d=pQk%2FYDfxyk1It%2BdH9Wj1W3wIqWfEp03u%2FOlStsvMnxY%3D&h=ca8ca00f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=KH4FjILxiUM</a><br />\n<br />\n我畀咗之前手足整嘅動畫畀佢哋睇<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qjRjgwR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqjRjgwR.jpg&h=c4b31512&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8MJmuSz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8MJmuSz.jpg&h=10ab2516&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n可能佢哋只係好行咁講兩句<br />\n但至少佢哋都知呢個係殺人政權<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37da2112b03df018ecaebd5444b2477cc860ac16","tid":1968581,"uid":54653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T18:57:09.000Z","msg":"Push盡做啦大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"447c94c0ffb0c33e02fd81178a9e115a7f70024a","tid":1968581,"uid":54653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T19:02:56.000Z","msg":"推唔郁<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3c47c252a1bf39b7cf652b6609dc1f7ef5599e9","tid":1968581,"uid":54653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T19:05:30.000Z","msg":"原來真係要做標題黨先得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75a73968478d5a22f9232b0875c75516e211b354","tid":1968581,"uid":54653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T19:08:24.000Z","msg":"連登仔好勁㗎嘛乜文都識<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n快啲輸出革命啦"},{"pid":"9a3116749c601d577ab6d359b726e16744e119fc","tid":1968581,"uid":54653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T19:11:44.000Z","msg":"幫手推啦"},{"pid":"4c35e05335e9d10a53d055de8f3a9679fcebeb3f","tid":1968581,"uid":54653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T19:16:33.000Z","msg":"我愛架妹<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a4720e4cf4205ece7726443e6cc4cf59b44063b","tid":1968581,"uid":345689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T19:17:14.000Z","msg":"P牌入嚟推一推<br />\n等我都搵番啲好耐無聯絡嘅外國朋友先"},{"pid":"8e89d3058a95e7314804b25b27a440bb61280099","tid":1968581,"uid":206715,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T19:17:52.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"38b9adb48a6e23661a69b2afa62acbb6ad173ef1","tid":1968581,"uid":54653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T19:19:29.000Z","msg":"本身公人為啲外國人好撚蠢唔識分香港人<br />\n點知佢哋好多都識㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79204eeba6179cba04efdf8e50e5434b8fdeab34","tid":1968581,"uid":54653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"38b9adb48a6e23661a69b2afa62acbb6ad173ef1","tid":1968581,"uid":54653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T19:19:29.000Z","msg":"本身公人為啲外國人好撚蠢唔識分香港人<br />\n點知佢哋好多都識㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T19:19:39.000Z","msg":"以為"},{"pid":"d343468388867b61e47185fe6defc3d1c98f04f4","tid":1968581,"uid":54653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T19:24:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：我 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：韓仔<br />\n韓仔：where r u from?<br />\n我：hong kong<br />\n韓仔：原來你就係所謂嘅香港er<br />\n我：係，我係香港er，唔係中國人<br />\n韓仔：明白了<br />\n<br />\n（翻譯自真實對話）<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4046851fd05084c8e5b2048b0b1bbc1afb619236","tid":1968581,"uid":54653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T19:28:17.000Z","msg":"使唔使咁撚多個廣州post上熱門牙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3388e10e0c2936204daf58eac2a0501997c3df3","tid":1968581,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"s